{"tid":2196512,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周庭個人資料被盜用登記做檢測 聶德權：再延長計劃非為「造靚條數」","createTime":"2020-09-10T03:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T11:27:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d91007facaeac4481a2ae07703b679c2b806764","tid":2196512,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"自 9 月 1 日普及社區檢測計劃推出以來，政府表示已錄得 128.3 萬人成功預約。前香港眾志成員周庭今早在 Facebook 表示，身份證號碼被盜用登記做檢測。公務員事務局局長聶德權今早在電台節目稱，局方發現 144 宗懷疑涉及盜用他人資料登記的個案。他強調社區檢測計劃以「願檢盡檢」為目標，並非只看參與人數，否認為「造靚條數」再延長計劃。<br />\n<br />\n周庭今早上在 Facebook 表示，昨日（9 月 9 日）突然收到個發自「HKSARG」的短訊，指其身份證號碼已登記參加社區檢測計劃，提醒她去大角咀體育館接受檢測。她立即感到「好奇怪」，「我根本就冇登記參加檢測，又點解會收到政府嘅短信呢？」她質疑身份證號碼出現「被登記」的情況，導致參與檢測人數存疑，「唔講仲以為係建制派搞緊簽名，咁搞法，你話有 13 億人參加檢測我都信啦」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E8%A2%AB%E7%9B%9C%E7%94%A8%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E5%81%9A%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E8%81%B6%E5%BE%B7%E6%AC%8A-%E5%86%8D%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E9%9D%9E%E7%82%BA-%E9%80%A0%E9%9D%9A%E6%A2%9D%E6%95%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%259B%259C%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25A8%2598%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC-%25E8%2581%25B6%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E9%2580%25A0%25E9%259D%259A%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%2595%25B8%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=26aa89eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%259B%259C%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25A8%2598%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC-%25E8%2581%25B6%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E9%2580%25A0%25E9%259D%259A%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%2595%25B8%2F&h=c98b4287\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E8%A2%AB%E7%9B%9C%E7%94%A8%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E5%81%9A%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E8%81%B6%E5%BE%B7%E6%AC%8A-%E5%86%8D%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E9%9D%9E%E7%82%BA-%E9%80%A0%E9%9D%9A%E6%A2%9D%E6%95%B8/</a>"},{"pid":"aeea814719d53ae2058e3c6626ce33ddeb69c973","tid":2196512,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T08:38:04.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b790a5545a1af78becf89fae874ad5531fee92ef","tid":2196512,"uid":365109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T11:27:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}